Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Royal wedding spectacle
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043wgjj
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 2 Aug 1981
Americans appreciate the spectacle of the royal wedding celebrations as Reagan brings glamour back to the White House. The sound quality on this recording is variable/poor. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less